Class CoderSizeEstimator<T>

  • java.lang.Object

    @Internal
public class CoderSizeEstimator<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements SizeEstimator<T>, java.io.Serializable
    This class is used to estimate the size in bytes of a given element. It uses the given Coder to calculate the size of the element.
